    public class RestADFBCXMLPersistenceManager
extends RestXMLPersistenceManager
    Implementation of Persistence manager interface that provides basic CRUD operations using the REST web services protocol against a remote server. The payload of the REST web service should be in ADF BC XML format, the format that is created by using the readXml and writeXMl API's on an ADF BC view object.
